key_inf: Starr Keys are needed to unlock Starr Drops after winning battles. They can contain resources, Hypercharges, portraits, and even brawlers (Legendary Starr).
cm_inf: The BOX may contain resources, Starrx, and brawlers: Colette, Kit, Bull, Edgar, Buzz, and Tick. With each opening, the reward multiplier decreases, and resets the next day.
mg_inf: The MEGA BOX contains all the rewards from Starr Drops â€” resources, brawlers, and even skins.

cm1_2: Well done, Bibi! I found a buff, do you need it?
cm1_4: Wait, what's happening to my screen...
cm2_2: Who were you talking about? Who's back?
cm3_2: Yes, how did you get here?
cm3_3: We were transported. I thought you were dead. Will you help us, sister?
cm3_5: Sorry I didn't tell you, brother(
cm4_1: One day, Bibi took you to the planet Starr. I couldn't find you until Lumi gave you away.
cm4_3: Well, I have to look after my family)
cm4_4: You abandoned us, and after Mom disappeared, you took over our home planet.
cm4_5: Because I want to destroy all the hedgehogs of Greenland!
cm4_6: And to help me with that...
cm5_1: What does all this mean, BIBI?!
cm5_2: Sorry, I was going to tell you, but later, when you grew up.
cm5_3: Strange that he's a hedgehog, and we're humans...
cm5_4: Our mom was a hedgehog. That's why we're different species.
cm6_2: Leave him, he needs to be alone.
cm6_4: But why did Bibi take me?
cm7_2: Give me the mother's gamepad - and you'll find out everything.
cm7_3: My gamepad? Why do you need it?
cm7_4: To destroy all the hedgehogs of Greenland!
cm8_2: No one killed me. Father locked me in a dungeon. I escaped and searched for you.
cm8_4: He tracked me and transported you here.
cm8_5: We need to find Jack before he's kidnapped.
cm9_1: What did you do to him?!
cm9_2: Improved him. And the Greenland gamepad is now mine!
cm9_4: It already has. By the way... I KILLED YOUR MOTHER AND JACK'S ENTIRE FAMILY!
cm9_6: Now Greenland is mine, and I'll destroy all the hedgehogs!!
cm10_3: It's fake! The real one was in my quills. Goodbye, daddy!
cm10_5: Jack, you saved us. I'm sorry for everything(
cm10_7: Lumi, will you come home with us?
